	Our People
    



















9d4b21c6-35a8-4ce7-97b5-772a310620b6






Our People
We believe that intellectual capital is critical to providing innovative solutions and, ultimately, having a positive economic impact.





Who We Are We believe that intellectual capital is critical to providing innovative solutions and, ultimately, having a positive economic impact. Over the years, we have been fortunate to attract some of the most talented professionals in our industry. They stay to build rewarding careers because of our entrepreneurial spirit, a commitment to our people and the high expectation for excellence. Our people are our most valuable asset – they are skilled problem solvers that believe challenges can be opportunities.  







				Mondays at Blackstone
			





 

 Accountability   Excellence   Integrity   Teamwork   Entrepreneurship  Everything we do is guided by this set of principles which define our character and culture; they have been at the core of Blackstone since its inception. These enduring qualities are the shared convictions that we bring to our professional and personal conduct – they are a fundamental strength of our business. 



 











